Horticulturists Rachel and Rodney Saunders were kidnapped, robbed and murdered near the Ongoye Forest near Mthunzini on the KwaZulu-Natal north coast. 

Magistrate Irfaan Khan said in his ruling that given the evidence against Safydeen Del Vecchio and his wife Fathima Patel , he believes it has become likely that they would try to flee. Dries Liebenberg  reports... --SABC--